{
  "texts": [
    "Use images and realia to support learning.\"",
    "Scoring of prompt output revealed high variance in scores within prompt groups (Figure 3).",
    "For example, scores resulting from P.1 ranged from 23/25 to 16/25, with an average score of 20.1/25.",
    "Likewise, scores for P.5, which contained the scoring criteria, ranged from a perfect score of 25/25 to 20/25.",
    "In general, outputs generated from identical prompts varied by at least five elements."
  ]
}